acdc.Core.Utils

Class Filter

  • java.lang.Object
    • acdc.Core.Utils.Filter

  • public class Filter
extends java.lang.Object
    Filter is a class used to check if a path is valid

    Filters available

    • Accepted extensions
    • Refused extensions
    • Refused files
    • By name
    • Last modified time
    • By weight
    • Superior weight
    • Inferior weight
    • Regex pattern
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Baptiste
